; C.R.A.P.maker Custom Start G-code
G21                                        ; set units to millimetres
G90                                        ; set to absolute positioning
M106 S0                                    ; set fan speed to zero (turned off)

G28                                        ; Home all axes
M420 S1                                    ; turn on mesh bed levelling if enabled in firmware

M75                                        ; start Print-Job-Timer

M117                                       ; Purge extruder
G92 E0                                     ; Reset Extruder

M117 Printing prime-line                   ; inform User
G1 Z2.0 F3000                              ; Move Z Axis up little to prevent scratching of Heat Bed
G1 X5 Y5 Z0.3 F5000.0                     ; Move to start position
G1 X200 Y5 Z0.3 F1500.0 E15              ; Draw the first line
G1 X200 Y5.4 Z0.3 F5000.0                ; Move to side a little
G1 X5 Y5.4 Z0.3 F1500.0 E30               ; Draw the second line

;G1 E-0.8 F3000                               ;retract a little

G92 E0                                     ; Reset Extruder
G1 Z5.0 F3000                              ; Move Z Axis up little to prevent scratching of Heat Bed
M117 Let's start!
; End of custom start GCode
